context.textAlign = 'left';

pos = pos.add(new Point(this.xPosition(), this.yPosition()));
this.gotoXY(pos.x, pos.y, false);
this.changed();

The direction of the text is the direction the sprite is facing, and color will match the pen color.</comment><header collabId="item_58_512"/><code collabId="item_58_511"/><inputs collabId="item_58_510"><input type="%txt" collabId="item_58_509">Hello!</input><input type="%n" collabId="item_58_508">12</input></inputs><script collabId="item_58_507"><block s="doRun" collabId="item_58_506"><block s="reportJSFunction" collabId="item_58_505"><list collabId="item_58_504"><l collabId="item_58_503">text</l><l collabId="item_58_502">size</l></list><l collabId="item_58_501">var stage = this.parentThatIsA(StageMorph),
    context = stage.penTrails().getContext('2d'),
    rotation = radians(this.direction() - 90),
    trans = new Point(
      this.center().x - stage.left(),
      this.center().y - stage.top()
    ),
    isWarped = this.Warped,
    len,
    pos;

if (isWarped) {endWarp(); }
context.save();
context.font = size + 'px monospace';
context.textAlign = 'left';
context.textBaseline = 'alphabetic';
context.fillStyle = this.color.toString();
len = context.measureText(text).width;
trans = trans.multiplyBy(1 / stage.scale);
context.translate(trans.x, trans.y);
context.rotate(rotation);
context.fillText(text, 0, 0);
context.translate(-trans.x, -trans.y);
context.restore();
pos = new Point(
  len * Math.sin(radians(this.direction())),
  len * Math.cos(radians(this.direction())));
pos = pos.add(new Point(this.xPosition(), this.yPosition()));
this.gotoXY(pos.x, pos.y, false);
this.changed();
if (isWarped) {this.startWarp(); }
stage.changed();</l></block><list collabId="item_58_500"><block var="text" collabId="item_58_499"/><block var="size"     context = stage.penTrails().getContext('2d'),
    rotation = radians(this.direction() - 90),
    trans = new Point(
      this.center().x - stage.left(),
      this.center().y - stage.top()
    ),
    isWarped = this.Warped,
    len,
    pos;

if (isWarped) {endWarp(); }
context.save();
context.font = size + 'px monospace';
context.textAlign = 'left';
context.textBaseline = 'alphabetic';
context.fillStyle = this.color.toString();
len = context.measureText(text).width;
trans = trans.multiplyBy(1 / stage.scale);
context.translate(trans.x, trans.y);
context.rotate(rotation);
context.fillText(text, 0, 0);
context.translate(-trans.x, -trans.y);
context.restore();
pos = new Point(
  len * Math.sin(radians(this.direction())),
  len * Math.cos(radians(this.direction())));
pos = pos.add(new Point(this.xPosition(), this.yPosition()));
this.gotoXY(pos.x, pos.y, false);
this.changed();
if (isWarped) {this.startWarp(); }

The direction of the text is the direction the sprite is facing, and color will match the pen color.</comment><header collabId="item_249_512"/><code collabId="item_249_511"/><inputs collabId="item_249_510"><input type="%txt" collabId="item_249_509">Hello!</input><input type="%n" collabId="item_249_508">12</input></inputs><script collabId="item_249_507"><block s="doRun" collabId="item_249_506"><block s="reportJSFunction" collabId="item_249_505"><list collabId="item_249_504"><l collabId="item_249_503">text</l><l collabId="item_249_502">size</l></list><l collabId="item_249_501">var stage = this.parentThatIsA(StageMorph),
    context = stage.penTrails().getContext('2d'),
    rotation = radians(this.direction() - 90),
    trans = new Point(
      this.center().x - stage.left(),
      this.center().y - stage.top()
    ),
    isWarped = this.Warped,
    len,
    pos;

if (isWarped) {endWarp(); }
context.save();
context.font = size + 'px monospace';
context.textAlign = 'left';
context.textBaseline = 'alphabetic';
context.fillStyle = this.color.toString();
len = context.measureText(text).width;
trans = trans.multiplyBy(1 / stage.scale);
context.translate(trans.x, trans.y);
context.rotate(rotation);
context.fillText(text, 0, 0);
context.translate(-trans.x, -trans.y);
context.restore();
pos = new Point(
  len * Math.sin(radians(this.direction())),
  len * Math.cos(radians(this.direction())));
pos = pos.add(new Point(this.xPosition(), this.yPosition()));
this.gotoXY(pos.x, pos.y, false);
this.changed();
if (isWarped) {this.startWarp(); }
stage.changed();</l></block><list collabId="item_249_500"><block var="text" collabId="item_249_499"/><block var="size" The direction of the text is the direction the sprite is facing, and color will match the pen color.</comment><header collabId="item_250_512"/><code collabId="item_250_511"/><inputs collabId="item_250_510"><input type="%txt" collabId="item_250_509">Hello!</input><input type="%n" collabId="item_250_508">12</input></inputs><script collabId="item_250_507"><block s="doRun" collabId="item_250_506"><block s="reportJSFunction" collabId="item_250_505"><list collabId="item_250_504"><l collabId="item_250_503">text</l><l collabId="item_250_502">size</l></list><l collabId="item_250_501">var stage = this.parentThatIsA(StageMorph),
    context = stage.penTrails().getContext('2d'),
    rotation = radians(this.direction() - 90),
    trans = new Point(
      this.center().x - stage.left(),
      this.center().y - stage.top()
    ),
    isWarped = this.Warped,
    len,
    pos;

if (isWarped) {endWarp(); }
context.save();
context.font = size + 'px monospace';
context.textAlign = 'left';
context.textBaseline = 'alphabetic';
context.fillStyle = this.color.toString();
len = context.measureText(text).width;
trans = trans.multiplyBy(1 / stage.scale);
context.translate(trans.x, trans.y);
context.rotate(rotation);
context.fillText(text, 0, 0);
context.translate(-trans.x, -trans.y);
context.restore();
pos = new Point(
  len * Math.sin(radians(this.direction())),
  len * Math.cos(radians(this.direction())));
pos = pos.add(new Point(this.xPosition(), this.yPosition()));
this.gotoXY(pos.x, pos.y, false);
this.changed();
if (isWarped) {this.startWarp(); }
stage.changed();</l></block><list collabId="item_250_500"><block var="text" collabId="item_250_499"/><block var="size"
